### **4. 29_LiveMetricRenderer**  
**Description:**  
Displays real-time streaming data as a continuously updating chart.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# LiveMetricRenderer - Real-Time Data Graphing

LiveMetricRenderer is a tool that visualizes incoming numeric values with a real-time line chart.

## Features
- Real-time animated chart  
- Adjustable update rate  
- Matplotlib-powered  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/29_LiveMetricRenderer.git
cd 29_LiveMetricRenderer
python visualize.py
